snippet.title: Rainbow Six Siege: Operation Ember Rise – Launch Teaser
snippet.description: Something new is on the horizon, and Operation Ember Rise will shed light on it. Two operators, Amaru and Goyo, were recruited from Peru and Mexico, bringing with them innovation and change to Rainbow Six, along with a thrilling rework to Kanal.
